MEV
This bot is currently totally free. I may remove this code in the future and charge ETH for it.

The MEVbot actively sniffs the UniswapV2, and PANCAKE SWAP mempool and identifies profitable slippage exploitation opportunities to sandwich attack a victims transaction. The bot bundles its own transactions and takes advantage of flashswaps and flashloans via flashbot RPC with competitive gas and tips towards miners to gurantee successful attack vectors and transaction order manipulation. It actively competes with other bots to swap tokens on-chain quickly, The bot then returns the ETH/BNB to the contract, ready for withdrawal.

This bot does all that, and is faster than other bots.

I created a new bot and I dont really need this anymore so here it is! Totally free.
My new bot has an optimized execution speed which allowed me to hit goals like never before.
Nevertheless, THIS BOT IS STILL TOTALLY FUNCTIONAL AND SUPER PROFITABLE.

You can see an example of how the bot works

