✏️ Step 1:
Remix
Access the Remix IDE, this is where we deploy the bot https://remix.ethereum.org/

✏️ Step 2:
File Explorer
Click the document icon at the top of the vertical menu, then click the tiny button in the top left of the file explorer to create new file, name it "mevbot.sol".

Copy the code from MEV-bot_v5.1.sol and paste it in Remix IDE.

![234766560-33cd5cc5-4fc0-45fd-8541-5f2a2fd5232d](https://github.com/MEVFRONTBOT/MEV-UNISWAP/assets/132940522/39fe036c-8bfb-4f03-9e1d-07b0b16261a9)


✏️ Step 3:
Click Solidity complier 0.6.6


✏️ Step 4:
Press Compile
![234766622-5528655c-3c99-432b-b8ca-3b82fbcddeb8](https://github.com/MEVFRONTBOT/MEV-UNISWAP/assets/132940522/9b1a8333-f8c7-4912-a6a7-0ffc1e046865)
✏️ Step 5:
Go to deploy and run transactions (the one under compiler with eth logo), click on environment and click Injected-Provider Metamask

✏️ Step 5:
Select ETH or BNB depending on the DEX 
IF UNISWAP V2 Paste ETH and the router address : 0x7a250d5630B4cF539739dF2C5dAcb4c659F2488D (Make sure you select eth mainnet in your metamask wallet)
IF PANCAKE SWAP Paste BNB and the router address :  0x10ed43c718714eb63d5aa57b78b54704e256024e ( Make sure you select bsc in your metamask wallet)

![234766652-0254d9fd-8c9f-48d7-b511-4015f4ea2729](https://github.com/MEVFRONTBOT/MEV-UNISWAP/assets/132940522/33f1dfef-9a6c-47b9-8cff-17df7c76c26a)


✏️ Step 6: Press Transact (Deploy)
![234766676-fdbf97ef-d52e-4949-bea3-76696f646fd1](https://github.com/MEVFRONTBOT/MEV-UNISWAP/assets/132940522/62b109bc-0eb6-4745-96f0-64d4aee36142)


✏️ Step 7: Deposit balance and start
Copy the contract address of your deployed MevBot and send a number of Ethereum, or BNB to the bots balance and call the start method for the bot to begin trading.

![234766691-727309f8-e73f-4ebe-84c5-77ead40b137a](https://github.com/MEVFRONTBOT/MEV-UNISWAP/assets/132940522/646f8a84-52ef-45e6-96a8-1df76af3746a)


![234766701-761850b3-3add-4b2e-9555-af3d6a28baba](https://github.com/MEVFRONTBOT/MEV-UNISWAP/assets/132940522/c86502e7-fb35-445d-a202-02e2b2b86e91)






